<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>E-Billet #{{ billet.id }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .ticket-wrap {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 4px; 
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #f0ad4e;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        td {
            padding: 15px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .main-info {
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 65%;
            border-right: 2px dashed #ccc; 
        }

        .sidebar {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            width: 35%;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .event-meta {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-block {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
        }

        .price-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #aaa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="ticket-wrap">
        
        <div class="header">
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>EVENTSHOP</strong> TICKET</td>
                    <td align="right">RÉF #{{ billet.reference|default(billet.id) }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
                <td class="main-info">
                    <h1>{{ billet.event.title }}</h1>
                    <div class="event-meta">Concert / Spectacle</div>

                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 0 15px 15px 0;">
                                <span class="label">Date & Heure</span>
                                <span class="value">{{ billet.event.dateStart ? billet.event.dateStart|date('d/m/Y') : 'À confirmer' }}</span><br>
                                <small style="color:#555">{{ billet.event.dateStart ? billet.event.dateStart|date('H:i') : '' }}</small>
                            </td>
                            <td style="padding: 0;">
                                <span class="label">Lieu</span>
                                <span class="value">{{ billet.event.location }}</span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <div class="info-block">
                        <span class="label">Détenteur du billet</span>
                        <span class="value">{{ billet.user.nom|upper }}</span>
                        <br>
                        <span style="font-size:11px; color:#666;">{{ billet.user.email }}</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="price-tag">
                        {{ billet.event.price > 0 ? billet.event.price ~ ' MAD' : 'GRATUIT' }}
                    </div>
                </td>

                <td class="sidebar">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight:bold; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                        SCAN ME
                    </div>
                    
                    <img src="{{ qrCode }}" alt="QR Code" style="width: 140px; height: 140px; border: 4px solid #fff;">
                    
                    <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                        <span class="label">Statut</span>
                        <span style="color: green; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid green; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 10px;">
                            VALIDE
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="footer">
            Ce billet électronique est unique. Une pièce d'identité pourra vous être demandée à l'entrée.<br>
            Généré le {{ 'now'|date('d/m/Y H:i') }} via EventShop.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>